videos.headline: Herbert drops dime for TD pass
videos.description: Oregon QB Justin Herbert throws a great pass to TE Dano Dillon for the 30-yard TD.

videos.headline: CAL QB scampers in for the 28-yard TD run
videos.description: CAL quarterback Brandon Mcllwain breaks a tackle and runs it in from 28 yards out for the TD.

videos.headline: Oregon RB takes off and scores the 45-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Oregon running back Travis Dye takes the handoff and bursts through the hole for the 45-yard TD.

videos.headline: Oregon recovers fumble and returns it 75 yards for TD
videos.description: Drayton Carlberg forces the fumble and La'Mar Winston picks it up and returns it 75 yards for the touchdown to put the Ducks up 28-10.

videos.headline: Oregon RB powers his way into end zone for the TD
videos.description: Oregon running back Cyrus Habibi-Likio bullies his way into the end zone for his 6th TD of the year.

videos.headline: CAL responds with a 10-yard TD run
videos.description: CAL running back rumbles in for the 10-yard touchdown cutting Oregon's lead to 35-17.

videos.headline: Cal's Duncan leaps for TD catch
videos.description: Cal wide receiver Jordan Duncan leaps over the defender and makes the touchdown catch cutting Oregon's lead to 35-24.

videos.headline: Oregon safety seals game with pick-6
videos.description: Oregon safety Ugochukwu Amadi picks off the pass and runs it back for a touchdown icing the game for the Ducks.
